title: Nyquist scores in OT, Wings beat Canucks 3-2
text: BING NEWS: Nyquist scores in OT, Wings beat Canucks 3-2 VANCOUVER, British Columbia (AP) -- Gustav Nyquist scored in overtime and the Detroit Red Wings beat the Vancouver Canucks 3-2 on Saturday night to end a four-game losing streak.
